Problem statement : Food Waste Redction solution

Introduction: Food waste is a major concern in India about  30 to 40 percent of food is wasted in india  everyday said by Food Safety And Standards Authority of India.
              it is a signicant problem in homes,restaurants,hostels that contributes to environmental pollution and resource depletion vast amount of food is wasted due to over preparation of food

Our solution to this problem:    We are planning to build a website where people can donate the leftover food .  Team will collect food from the hotels,homes..etc and distribute to the orphanages and people who are in hunger.
                                 people who donate food will be rewarded with food points,
